00:05:04.770 --> 00:05:06.840 align:middle line:10%
Leading American
scientist Dr. Bruce

00:05:06.840 --> 00:05:09.780 align:middle line:10%
Damer is at Rotorua's
Hell's Gate conducting

00:05:09.780 --> 00:05:13.530 align:middle line:10%
research trials aiming to
answer the age old question,

00:05:13.530 --> 00:05:14.850 align:middle line:10%
how did we get here?

00:05:14.850 --> 00:05:15.880 align:middle line:10%
- It's very exciting.

00:05:15.880 --> 00:05:18.690 align:middle line:10%
It's a 21st century science,
revolutionary science,

00:05:18.690 --> 00:05:19.920 align:middle line:10%
to watch.

00:05:19.920 --> 00:05:22.950 align:middle line:10%
If we can find this cycle,
it's the engine of creation,

00:05:22.950 --> 00:05:23.760 align:middle line:10%
effectively.

00:05:23.760 --> 00:05:27.060 align:middle line:10%
Also that we came not
from an individual,

00:05:27.060 --> 00:05:30.810 align:middle line:10%
